chland‘ angenommen. Es erscheint als Band 2 in der Buchreihe MAECENATA SCHRIFTEN. Weitere Informationen unter www.maecenata.eu  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / General.2bisacsh  aBürgerschaftliches Engagement.  aKulturfinanzierung.  aKulturförderung.  aSpende.1 aStrachwitz, Rupert Graf, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Social Sciences 2000 - 2014z9783110638080oZDB-23-GSS08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruyterteBook-Paket Best of Lucius & Luciusz97831105150770 cprintz978382820430040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311051022540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110510225423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110510225/original  a978-3-11-051507-7  eBook-Paket Best of Lucius & Lucius  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-GSSc2000d2014